For productGroupNumber only = and "and" operators are supported and only name field is supported along with productGroupNumber. An example would be productGroupNumber=1 and name='rrr' An example of a single where query would be name = 'Timer samlet' . An example of a multiple where query would be name = 'Timer samlet' AND costPrice= 1

parameters.description: Specify a field sort order for the response payload. To sort descending by name would be, -name . Without specifying desc (-), default is ascending

parameters.description: The next page cursor, taken from the response header elements-next-page-token
